          "_name": "features7",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"features6\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <!---->\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Cost\" name=\"showCost\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"cardsBg\" value=\"#fafafa\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#fafafa\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#bed3f9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid' : fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"row align-items-center\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverseContent}\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                    <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                        <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/square-flyer-mulku-696x696.png\" alt>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n                    <div class=\"text-box\">\n                        <h5 class=\"mbr-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n                            <b>Cleaning Notebook</b></h5>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .cost, .mbr-section-btn\">Notebook/laptop mengalami panas (overheat) dapat juga mengakibatkan performa dari kualitas suatu Notebook/Laptop berkurang, dan terkadang hal tersebut membuat kita kurang nyaman dalam menggunakan notebook/laptop untuk bekerja ataupun belajar.<br><br>Dengan dibersihkan bagian dalam komponen notebook/laptop secara berkala dapat menghindari masalah panas (overheat) pada notebook. Oleh karena itu kami berikan solusi untuk Anda bilamana notebook/laptop Anda perlu di bersihkan agar terhindar dari masalah tersebut.<br><br>Selama bulan promo kami berikan harga spesial untuk Anda yang memerlukan jasa dari kami.<br><br></p>\n                        <div class=\"cost\" mbr-if=\"showCost\">\n                            <span mbr-text mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" class=\"currentcost mbr-fonts-style pr-2\" data-app-selector=\".currentcost\">R35K</span>\n                            <span mbr-text mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" class=\"oldcost mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".oldcost\">Rp70K</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn pt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=6282122872332&text=Halo%20CS%20Mulku,%20saya%20ingin%20promo%20CLEANING%20notebook%20saya\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">Pesan sekarang</a></div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
