          "_name": "features12",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"features11\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" plugins=\"mobirise-icons2\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Items\" name=\"showLink\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background3.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\" mbr-class=\"{'offset-lg-1': fullWidth}\">\n                <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-box\">\n                            <b>Misi Perusahaan</b></h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .link-wrap, .mbr-section-btn\"></p>\n                        <div class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style counter-container\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showLink\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                            <ul>\n                                <li>Memberikan pelayanan terbaik serta menjaga kepercayaan mitra bisnis</li>\n                                <li>Menjadikan mitra bisnis sebagai prioritas utama dengan menyediakan barang ataupun jasa yang berkualitas</li>\n                                <li>Menjaga kode etik pada setiap proses bisnis perusahaan</li>\n                            </ul>\n                        </div>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                            <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">View all our features</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} md-pb\">\n                <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                    <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/name-card-mulku-2000x2252.png\" alt=\"Mulku Technologies\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
